  FLUX-CiM's dataset for [ <A HREF="flux-cim-cs.out.xml">300 computer
  science references</A> ] [ <A HREF="flux-cim-med.out.xml">2000 medical
  references</A> ] [ <A HREF="cora.out.xml">on the CORA dataset</A> ].
  Note that these results are considered cheating as current version
  has been trained on this data.
</ul>

